{"tid":847211,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就嚟懷疑自己有情緒病","createTime":"2018-10-04T04:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T16:22:26.000Z","uid":10759,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb575c371ec94189ce77bc441027220d9d9c815","tid":847211,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"隔好幾日就會自己沉咗落勁負面嘅情緒<br />\n成個人都好depress<br />\n因為啲好小嘅事都好唔開心<br />\n無啦啦都可以有眼淚流出嚟<br />\n一路自己諗又會一路係到流眼淚<br />\n對住人又要扮無嘢開心心咁<br />\n一到自己一個又瘋狂開始亂諗<br />\n對住啲信任嘅朋友又好任性地發咗佢哋脾氣<br />\n其實個心好愧疚 點解要人受你啲脾氣<br />\n唔想麻煩佢哋 好想柄埋自己<br />\n救命啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cac10e4c5037e15319033a4000c92a2f1334e2","tid":847211,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"087727eef3935f67e8e12b940ed62440720764c9","tid":847211,"uid":194318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"I know that feel, bro."},{"pid":"3d17c3bdf4f7ce9e744821a9b1156a813bfdd100","tid":847211,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"好肚餓又好唔開心 屌"},{"pid":"aeadc007154fff56692db522a1aad1a4b664db44","tid":847211,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cac10e4c5037e15319033a4000c92a2f1334e2","tid":847211,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:16:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"Dllmo"},{"pid":"d72531d4f9ccf41a14eb96c21b209301f6f92c49","tid":847211,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"087727eef3935f67e8e12b940ed62440720764c9","tid":847211,"uid":194318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"I know that feel, bro."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.